song.title: Psychotic Breakdown (Reject Your Mind 2010 Mix)
song.info: This is a collaboration between me (Spiral) and Tranceptor made in 1999. Now, 11 years later the track was reinserted and enhanced to get a bit MOAR UNZ! :D Spiral Tranception are: Leo "Tranceptor" Savela & Mats "Spiral" Antonsson.
